    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a Variable M Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the torsional loads of spirited cornering. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precision of the McPherson strut front and multi-link rear arrangement. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car ready for its next apex.",
