      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior features a deep Obsidian Black metallic finish that retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Charcoal leather interior remains supple and smoke-free; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light bolster wear, while the rear seats appear nearly untouched. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, having received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake pad replacement. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. It sits on original alloy wheels wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
